{"tid":1236573,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要求林奠特赦義士 同意請幫推","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T02:10:13.000Z","uid":110430,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5085e598f0062e77bead7959059c2a30d27c06ef","tid":1236573,"uid":110430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/184695195665625/posts/449381479196994?s=100034683034432&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F184695195665625%2Fposts%2F449381479196994%3Fs%3D100034683034432%26sfns%3Dmo&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=109951e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/184695195665625/posts/449381479196994?s=100034683034432&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有人講稿都諗埋</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">『各位市民、警察、記者朋友，關於6.9、6.12、6.16的事件，政府將之定性為一場「衝突」，「衝突」中做成不少人命的傷亡，政府深表難過及抱歉。經此「事件」，特區政府深切反省，以我本人為首的工作，無論方向與執行都出現嚴重失誤，才會嚴重破壞市民對特區政府的信任。為此，本人決定特赦所有於16.9、6.12、6.16「衝突」中曾使用過度武力的市民和警察，並且重新制定警察處理大型集會/遊行/騷亂等行動策略，以使香港的政治與經濟發展重回正軌。完成相關工作後，我們辭去行政長官的職務，重啟選舉程序，以選出賢能繼續帶領香港，服務市民。』<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">起碼大家救左義士先<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"817dcc24d2b9f55716a0db4e3c824dc942a49f0b","tid":1236573,"uid":110430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:42:08.000Z","msg":"利申： 我唔係果位版主"},{"pid":"f0d6b139e627c282073aacd3604b1f6816301e48","tid":1236573,"uid":110430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"推到林奠特赦義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da7b8ce4e65feb0a3b0a9ebf7de69654728c12b","tid":1236573,"uid":110430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"推到林奠特赦義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class